# Changelog

Dieses Changelog spiegelt die GitHub Release Notes 1:1 (Markdown) aus `templui/templui`.
Last synced: 2026-02-16

## v1.5.0 (2026-02-08)

Source: https://github.com/templui/templui/releases/tag/v1.5.0

## What's Changed

- CLI: Added `--installed` for bulk component updates via `templui --installed add[@<ref>]` (#494)
- CLI: Removed short-form aliases (`-f`, `-v`, `-h`, `-m`) in favor of explicit long flags (#494)
- selectbox: Added a clear button in the trigger for faster value reset (#496)
- selectbox: Improved keyboard/focus behavior when `nosearch` is enabled (#492)
- selectbox: Simplified selected-state handling using Tailwind/data-attribute conditionals instead of JS toggling (#498)
- timepicker: Preselected hour/minute values are now auto-scrolled into view when opening (#491)
- toast: Fixed initialization for toasts on full page loads (#493)
- docs: Updated progress examples to match the current API

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/templui/templui/compare/v1.4.0...v1.5.0

