## v0.40.0 (2025-03-21)

Source: https://github.com/templui/templui/releases/tag/v0.40.0

# Release v0.40.0: Component Composition & Better Semantics

This is my biggest release so far with many changes! It's mainly about converting all components where possible and sensible to component composition for better customization, accessibility, and so on - you know what I mean! Also, this is another big step towards v1.0!

## 🔄 Major Changes (101 commits, 291 files changed)

* **rename Sheet component to Drawer** for more semantic naming
* **remove all comments from component structure** to have cleaner and more readable code
* **docs(button):** improve showcase for htmx loading button example with native tailwindcss instead of additional css script
* **fix(charts):** use correct charts.js cdn to avoid browser console errors
* **feat(form/toast):** use enums instead of raw strings for component configuration
* **chore(components):** global renaming from Type to Variant for config props on all components to be more "semantic"
* **docs:** better internal file structure and naming

## 🏗️ Component Architecture Overhaul

* **chore(components):** big update on almost all components (Attention many breaking changes!) and improve docs showcases:
  * use component composition style instead of content passing via props on: Accordion, Avatar, Badge, Breadcrumb, Button (can now be disabled even with Href prop), Tooltip, dropdown menu (generally improved with scrolling), Pagination, Select, Label, Carousel, Form, Drawer, Input OTP, Radio Card, Checkbox Card, Rating, Slider (also use vanilla instead of Alpinejs), Tabs

* **feat(timepicker):** remove it for now because of compatibility problems
* **add new component: Table** (shoutout to @niclimcy)
* **feat(modal):** Added Modal Closing Control Options:
  * DisableClickAway: Prevents modal from closing when clicking outside
  * DisableESC: Prevents modal from closing when pressing ESC key 
  * (shoutout to @derkan)

## 🧰 Improvements & Refinements

* **docs:** change navbar and announcmentbar style
* **feat(label):** replace Alpinejs with vanillajs
* **chore(helpers):** sort alphabetically
* **feat(button):** add tailwind ring when button is active
* **feat(Toast):** better API and showcase
* **chore(components):** add base props (id, class, attributes) to every component for better customization
* **feat(spinner):** remove unnecessary Text prop
* **chore(utils):** better utils comments
* **feat(Tooltip):** rename prop TooltipSide to TooltipPosition
* **chore(all components):** better sorting for consistency and readability: types, templ components, scripts, functions and methods
* **chore:** remove postfix on some components, removed the word Root on base components
* **feat(Rating):** has cursor pointer now
* **chore(utils):** rename TwIf and TfIfElse to If and IfElse and make them more generic
* **feat(Avatar):** add avatar group and improve showcase examples
* **docs:** more semantic showcase example titles
* **docs:** Form and Label showcase links are now complete and alphabetically sorted
* **docs:** add examples for Form and Label on all form related components now
* **feat(separator):** add labels and improve showcase examples
* **chore:** use string enums instead of iota in all components now

## Upgrade
```
go get github.com/axzilla/templui@v0.40.0
go mod tidy
```

